The elasticStack helm repo is 

 https://helm.elastic.co

 helm repo add aliasname https://helm.elastic.co

  let the aliasname be elastic

  helm repo add elastic https://helm.elastic.co

3. update the repo by running 

helm repo update

to verify the addition of the helm-elastic repo, run

helm repo add

This elasticStack helm REPO, you can install EFK (elasticSearch, FileBreats and Kibana) by searching for each of their chartName by running

helm search repo repoName

and then install by running

helm install NAME chartName
